Nippon Shinpan Co Ltd &lt;NSHT.T> has agreedwith &lt;Mastercard International> to issue a new credit cardcalled Nippon Shinpan-Master Joint Card for use in Japan andabroad, a Nippon Shinpan spokesman said.    The card, to be issued within the year, will be honoured atMastercard-affiliated outlets in 160 countries and at locationsaccepting the Nippon Shinpan card, he said.    Nippon Shinpan reached a similar agreement with &lt;VisaInternational> on September 29. REUTER&#3;